{"id": "art-2371", "label": "Art. 2371", "title": "Art. 2371", "slug": "art-2371", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1344645905\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1864\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1344645905\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 237<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_66766810\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1863\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_66766810\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Atunci când un asociat r&#259;spunde nelimitat pentru <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\npe durata <span class=SpellE>func&#355;ion&#259;rii</span> acesteia,\nr&#259;spunderea sa pentru aceste <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;ii</span> va\nfi nelimitat&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în faza dizolv&#259;rii <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dac&#259; este cazul, a lichid&#259;rii <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1015042771\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1862\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1015042771\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Atunci când, pe durata <span class=SpellE>func&#355;ion&#259;rii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, un asociat r&#259;spunde pentru\n<span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span> acesteia în limitele aportului la\ncapitalul social, r&#259;spunderea sa va fi limitat&#259; la acest aport <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> în <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span>\ndizolv&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dac&#259; este cazul, a\nlichid&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_81473329\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1861\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_81473329\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Asociatul care, în frauda creditorilor, abuzeaz&#259; de\ncaracterul limitat al r&#259;spunderii sale <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nde personalitatea juridic&#259; distinct&#259; a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nr&#259;spunde nelimitat pentru <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span>\nneachitate ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> dizolvate,\nrespectiv lichidate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1290114740\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1860\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1290114740\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)R&#259;spunderea asociatului devine nelimitat&#259; în <span\nclass=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> alin. (3), în special atunci când acesta\ndispune de bunurile <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> ca <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cum ar fi bunurile sale proprii sau dac&#259;\ndiminueaz&#259; activul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> în\nbeneficiul personal ori al unor <span class=SpellE>ter&#355;i</span>, cunoscând\nsau trebuind s&#259; cunoasc&#259; faptul c&#259; în acest mod societatea nu va\nmai fi în m&#259;sur&#259; s&#259; <span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> execute <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span>.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}